# ============================================================
# CIVILIZATION TRUTH BOUNDARY POLICY
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: 080.policy
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Define policy rules for truth-boundary protection.

policy_rules:
- reflected state must never silently become canonical truth
- cross-domain synchronization must not transfer truth ownership implicitly
- derived state must preserve source lineage
- operational state must remain operational unless explicitly constitutionalized

prohibited:
- hidden truth reassignment
- silent overwrite of subordinate domain truth
- unmarked reflected-state promotion
